main event: A citizen reported a sighting of a green rocket rising vertically from the surface at a distance of 25 to 32 miles.
interesting points: The sighting occurred on 16 November 1953 at 1647Z,The object was observed to rise vertically and then descend back to the surface,The report was transmitted to various military and intelligence organizations including the CIA and Navy,The sighting was made from a considerable distance of 25-30 miles,The photographer at the scene did not see the object after the initial sighting.
